        <item>
            <title>Version 0.4.0</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 05:43:09 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>7</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.4.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<style>code{background:rgba(127,127,127,.15);padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;}ul,ol{padding-left:1.2em;}</style>
<h2>What&#x27;s Changed</h2>
<h2>New</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Snippets panel in the right sidebar, with a dedicated editor window and View/Find menu commands</li>
  <li>Snippets and snippet groups are saved to settings and survive export/import</li>
  <li>Connection icon now appears in the tab bar, left of the tab title</li>
</ul>
<h2>Fixes</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Sidebar edge no longer oscillates when hovering near the resize zone</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Full Changelog</strong>: https://github.com/babul/quay/compare/v0.3.0...v0.4.0</p>
            ]]></description>
